  "title": "Treatment of periodontal disease for glycaemic control in people with diabetes",
  "abstract": "This is a protocol for a Cochrane Review (Intervention). The objectives are as follows: The null hypothesis is: Periodontal therapy has no effect on glycaemic control in people with diabetes. The objectives are: To investigate the association between periodontal therapy and glycaemic control in people with diabetes. To identify whether further research is required in this area and if so, to identify the important research questions and appropriate study designs.",
